name: TicketHurry
overview: TicketHurry is a marketplace that gives consumers an easier and safer way to purchase from licensed ticket brokers. TicketHurry provides a safety net to consumers by providing them with a satisfaction guarantee that would not come from direct sellers or ticket scalpers. TicketHurry carries readily available and hard to find tickets, using many different networks to provide them. Tickets sold by TicketHurry’s sources may be sold for less or more than their face value depending on demand. TicketHurry operates within a vast network of ticket contacts, including record labels, season ticket holders, Fan Clubs, individual ticket resellers, and ticket brokers.
